I really loved the first Grim Legends a little bit more, but this was still very well done. In many of this type, the storyline is just kind of the thing that glues the HOG and minigames together and there's not much more attention paid. In this one, the story is an integral part of the game and is woven through the minigames and HOG. I am normally pretty cynical but was actually getting sad when the swan brothers kept dying in their efforts to thwart the dark swan and evil sorceress. Definitely a winner.

No glitches on Galaxy Pro 12.1 tablet. 5 stars.
